Package ariba.ui.outline Description

Controls for creating oulines (like a tree control).

w: namespace -- Namespace aware templates typically refer to these components with the "w:" prefix (e.g.<w:OutlineControl/>)

Note that while w:OutlineControl can be used in concert with w:OutlineRepetition, it is most often used in the first column of an t:DataTable to create an outline table.

See Also:
ariba.ui.table
